column1: FOR THE YEARS ENDED DECEMBER 31, 2025 TO 2029

The following Unaudited Projected Pro Forma Financial Statements (the “Proforma Financials”) contains unaudited projected pro forma income statements of 2661707 Alberta Ltd for the years ended December 31, 2025,2026,2027,2028 and 2029, unaudited projected pro forma statements of financial position as of December 31, 2025, 2026, 2027, 2028 and 2029, and unaudited projected pro forma statements of cashflow for the years ended December 31, 2025,2026,2027,2028 and 2029.
The Proforma Financials have been derived from assumptions described below and have also been derived from and should be read in conjunction with the following documents:
- The internally prepared economics prepared by Management of 2661707
